<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root {
    --bg-cream: #fdf9f3;
    --accent-orange: #ff9d5c;
    --light-orange: #fbdac3;
    --font-poppins: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    --font-serif: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }

  .custom-benefit-section {
    background-color: var(--bg-cream);
    padding: 100px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-poppins);
  }

  /* Main Headline - Bold Poppins */
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-poppins);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    color: #000;
  }

  .benefit-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 40px 30px;
    max-width: 900px; /* Reduced width to prevent cards from being "Too Big" */
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 50px 40px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    /* Soft shadow to match the image style */
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Centering the 3rd card at the bottom */
  .benefit-card:nth-child(3) {
    grid-column: 1 / span 2;
    justify-self: center;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px; 
  }

  /* Badges (Overlapping Circles) */
  .number-badge {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    position: relative;
    height: 44px;
    width: 70px;
  }

  .badge-main, .badge-secondary {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: white;
    position: absolute;
  }

  .badge-main {
    background: var(--accent-orange);
    z-index: 2;
    left: 0;
  }

  .badge-secondary {
    background: var(--light-orange);
    z-index: 1;
    left: 26px; 
  }

  /* Card Headlines - Using Serif Font for "Czech/Elegant" look */
  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 24px;
    margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000;
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-poppins);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 320px;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .benefit-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .benefit-card:nth-child(3) {
      grid-column: 1;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="custom-benefit-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Además de la guía también obtendrás...</h2>

  <div class="benefit-container">
    
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="number-badge">
        <div class="badge-main">01</div>
        <div class="badge-secondary">03</div>
      </div>
      <h3>Contacto por WhatsApp</h3>
      <p>Si te surgen dudas, escríbenos sin compromiso. Queremos que tengas toda la información clar</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="number-badge">
        <div class="badge-main">03</div>
        <div class="badge-secondary">03</div>
      </div>
      <h3>Descuento directo</h3>
      <p>Si decides dar el salto a  nuestro programa de acompañamiento, descontamos el importe de la guía del precio final.
</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="number-badge">
        <div class="badge-main">02</div>
        <div class="badge-secondary">03</div>
      </div>
      <h3>Actualizaciones incluidas</h3>
      <p>La guía se renueva periódicamente para que siempre tengas datos reales y actuales.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>